\c 23 1 Zvino ndiwo mashoko okupedzisira aDhavhidhi, Zvanzi naDhavhidhi mwanakomana waJese, Zvanzi nomunhu wakakudzwa kwazvo, Naiye muzodzwa waMwari waJakobho, Muimbi wezvakanaka waIsiraeri, 2 "Mweya waJehovha wakataura mukati mangu, Shoko rake rakanga riri parurimi rwangu. 3 Mwari waIsiraeri wakataura, dombo raIsiraeri rakataura neni, rikati, `Mumwe uchavapo, uchabata vanhu zvakarurama, Uchabata ushe achitya Mwari; 4 Uchava sechiedza chamangwanani, kana zuva robuda, Samangwanani kana kusina makore. Kana bumhudza richibuda pavhu
